enpilink
========

enpilink is an enpitech-branded, account-free fork of Skybridge.

Forked from alpic-ai/skybridge (https://github.com/alpic-ai/skybridge),
licensed under the MIT License. The original copyright notice is retained in
the LICENSE file.

  Copyright (c) 2025 Alpic — original Skybridge framework (MIT)
  Copyright (c) 2026 enpitech — enpilink fork and modifications

enpilink removes the Alpic/Skybridge cloud-account couplings (telemetry,
metrics, hosted tunnel/playground/audit, and deploy integrations) and rebrands
the project to enpitech. It otherwise preserves the upstream architecture and
API surface.
